Resource Profile: CCG IPS Bundle

Official URL: https://profiles.ihe.net/QRPH/CCG/StructureDefinition/ccg-di-ips-bundle Version: 1.0.0-comment
Active as of 2025-05-20 Computable Name: CCG_IPS_Bundle

This bundle follows the IPS Bundle with the exception of using the CCG Composition

Usage:

  • Use this Resource Profile: CCG Data In Bundle
